
0.90 (April 2009)

- Added tag 'nodiary' or 'nd' for items that should not show in remind
- Generalized year guessing 
- Modifications by Michael J. Bruderer - allow adding an item like:
   add a todo-item with the command ptodo -a in 2 days [ some tags] "my meeting with joe" 
- Colour syntax file for vim
- Added symbols for indented lines 
- Multi line support (indented lines are part of a container)
